Message-ID: <1pqruhINNksi@srvr1.engin.umich.edu>
References: <1993Apr2.103536.801@batman.bmd.trw.com> <93092.144958J5J@psuvm.psu.edu> <1993Apr2.155057.808@batman.bmd.trw.com>
