References: <1pan4f$b6j@fido.asd.sgi.com> <1pcqf3INNqt7@gap.caltech.edu> <11703@vice.ICO.TEK.COM> <930401.113200.2K4.rusnews.w165w@mantis.co.uk> <1pignpINNsp9@gap.caltech.edu>
Date:  6 Apr 93 03:35:07 GMT
