Subject: Re: The Inimitable Rushdie (Re: An Anecdote about Islam
Message-ID: <930406.111336.1D8.rusnews.w165w@mantis.co.uk>
Date: Tue, 6 Apr 1993 11:13:36 GMT
References: <113750@bu.edu> <1phkf7INN86p@dsi.dsinc.com> <114133@bu.edu>
