References: <8feu_KO00XsF0kpc5p@andrew.cmu.edu> <1993Apr03.001125.23294@watson.ibm.com> <1pq5e8INNh73@dsi.dsinc.com> <1993Apr08.174942.45124@watson.ibm.com>
